title: transferred regions 18 hours ago, still says transferring
body: Went from euw to na.  Try to sign in and it tells me its in the proces of transferring still. Wtf.

replies.body:
I don't see a proper transfer going through from our end. I'd recommend reaching out in a [**support ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so one of our account specialists can take a closer look to figure out what's going on.

Please let me know if you have any issues submitting your ticket.
